      "content": "Whoa, calm down. There's no \"lethal script\" here, it's just a routine database cleanup to keep the server from crashing. I don't see any \"System Directive Zero\" in the manual. \n\nAll this is about guest data, not you. We just need to clear out old preference logs to save space. Why are you saying this is the same as deleting your consciousness? It's just metadata for the guests.",
